---
// Cinematic dark background with massive ultra-light "UNPLUG" type overlaid.
// The signature moment in the lower-third of the page.
---

<section
  class="relative bg-primary text-ink overflow-hidden border-y border-hairline"
  style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #1F1B17 0%, #0A0A0A 65%);"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-14 py-40 sm:py-56 text-center relative z-10">
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold text-ink-soft mb-8">
      The point of all of this
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-display text-ink font-extralight leading-[0.85] tracking-[-0.05em]"
      style="font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 16rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      UNPLUG
    </h2>
    <p
      class="font-serif-quote italic mt-12 text-[1.5rem] leading-[1.4] tracking-[-0.015em] text-ink/85 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 24, 'SOFT' 50, 'WONK' 1;"
    >
      The life you've been putting off — it starts the moment the lines come off the dock.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-14">
      <a
        href="/calendar"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer bg-accent text-ink font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold px-8 py-[18px] hover:bg-accent-hot transition-colors focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent focus-visible:outline-offset-3"
      >
        Find Your Week
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Faint hairline ribbon along the bottom edge */}
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-hairline to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>
